 Educational Background



 


California State University - Los Angeles

                  California State University, Los Angeles has one of the most diverse student populations of any college or university in the nation. The University is committed to free scholarly inquiry, to high-quality teaching, and to academic excellence in undergraduate, graduate, and other post-baccalaureate and extended education programs.                





 Career History



Chief Executive Officer & President

                                    2011 - Current                


Nova Lifestyle, Inc.


                  Nova Lifestyle, Inc. designs, markets and manufactures modern home furniture. Its collections of lifestyle furniture brands include diamond sofa, colorful world, giorgio mobili and other. The company sells products under the brand name, diamond sofa. Nova Lifestyle was founded by Ya Ming Wong and Yuen Ching Ho in 1992 and is headquartered in Commerce, CA.                




Chief Executive Officer

                                    1992 - Prior                


Diamond Bar Outdoors, Inc.


                  Diamond Bar Outdoors, Inc., part of Nova Lifestyle, Inc., is a company headquartered in Commerce, CA, involved in wood office furniture. The firm was founded by Thanh H. Lam. Diamond Bar Outdoors, Inc. was acquired by Nova Lifestyle, Inc. on 31 Aug 11 for $0.45 million.                





